Name: Escort Towage Commenced
Description: Escort tug connected to vessel or Escort towage operation commence

Name: Escort Towage Completed
Description: Escort tug disconnected to vessel or Escort towage operation completed

Name: Departure Anchoring Operation Commenced
Description: Start heaving up anchor  (an anchoring spot is a berth and req/conf departure as such)

Name: Arrival Vessel Berth
Description: Vessels arrived to assigned berth (could also capture anchoring area if no distinction is made between berth and anchorage area in sending system)

Name: Departure Vessel Berth
Description: Vessels departed from berth (could also capture anchoring area if no distinction is made between berth and anchorage area)

Name: Arrival Tug TugZone
Description: Tug arrived to tug zone (during departure) / Tug arrivals to tug zone

Name: Arrival Vessel TugZone
Description: Vessel arrived to tug zone (during departure) / Vessel arrives to tug zone

Name: Departure Vessel TugZone
Description: Vessel departed from tug zone (with or without towage)

Name: Arrival EscortTug Tug zone
Description: Escort tug arrived to vessel in tug zone

Name: Departure EscortTug Tug Zone
Description: Escort tug departed from vessel in tug zone

Name: Arrival EscortTug EscortTugZone
Description: Escort tug arrived to vessel at escort tug zone

Name: Departure EscortTug EscortTugZone
Description: Escort tug departed from vessel at escort tug zone

Name: Arrival Vessel EscortTugZone
Description: Vessel arrived at Escort tug zone

Name: Departure Vessel Escort Tug zone
Description: Vessel departed from escort tug zone (with or without escort)

Name: Pilotboat Departure from Pilot Boarding Area
Arrival Vessel PilotBoardingArea
Description: Vessel arrived to PBA during arrival/departure

Name: Departure Vessel PilotBoardingArea
Description: Vessel departed from PBA during arrival/departure

Name: Arrival Escort Tug Vessel
Description: EscortTug has arrived to the vessel

Name: Arrival IceBreaker Vessel
Description: IceBreaker has arrived to the vessel

Name: Departure IceBreaker Vessel
Description: IceBreaker departed from Vessel, mission completed, aborted

Name: Arrival Tug Vessel
Description: The tugboat has arrived to the vessel

Name: Departure Tug Vessel
Description: Tug and vessel has been disconnected

Name: Bunker Vessel Alongside Vessel
Description: Bunker vessel is alongside the vessel

Name: Bunker Vessel Departed Vessel
Description: Bunker vessel has departed the Vessel

Name: Sludge Vessel Departed Vessel
Description: Sludge vessel has departed the vessel

Name: Slop Vessel Departed Vessel
Description: Slop vessel has departed the vessel

Name: Water Vessel Departed Vessel
Description: Water vessel has departed the vessel

Name: Pilot Boat Departed Vessel
Description: Pilot boat has departed the vessel

Name: Arrival Vessel Traffic Area
Description: The vessel entered the VTS Traffic area of the port

Name: Departure Vessel TrafficArea
Description: Vessel departed from VTS traffic area

Name: Arrival Vessel Port Area
Description: The vessel entered the Port Area (inner line)

Name: Departure Vessel Port Area
Description: The vessel departs from the Port Area (inner line)

Name: Arrival Tug HomeBase
Description: Tug has arrived to Home base

Name: Departure Tug HomeBase
Description: Tug has departed from Home base

Name: Arrival PilotBoat HomeBase
Description: Pilot boat has arrived to Home base

Name: Departure PilotBoat HomeBase
Description: Pilot boat has departed to Home base

Name: Arrival PilotBoat HomeBase
Description: Pilot has arrived to Home Base

Name: Departure PilotBoat HomeBase
Description: Pilot has departed from Home Base

Name: Departure Rendezvous Area
Description: IceBreaker departed rendezvous area, with or without vessels connected.

Name: Departure Rendezvous Area
Description: Vessel departed rendezvous area, following alone/convoy or connected to IceBreaker

Name: Arrival IceBreaker LOC
Description: Icebreaker arrived to an unspecified location

Name: Departure IceBreaker LOC
Description: IceBreaker departed from current LOC (unspecified) to transit to Vessel

Name: Arrival Vessel LOC
Description: Vessel arrived to an unspecified location

Name: Departure Vessel LOC
Description: Vessel departed from a particular (unspecified) location

Name: Arrival Pilotboat LOC
Description: Pilotboat arrived to an unspecified location

Name: Arrival Escort Tug LOC
Description: Escort tug arrived to an unspecified location

Name: Departure Escort Tug LOC
Description: Escort tug transited from previous (unspecified) location to its next towage operation

Name: Arrival Tug LOC
Description: Tug arrived to an unspecified location

Name: Departure Tug LOC
Description: Tug transited from previous (unspecified) location to its next towage operation

Name: Escort Towage Requested
Description: A request for Escort towage has been made

Name: Escort Towage Request Received
Description: A request for Escort towage has been received

Name: Escort Towage Request Denied
Description: A request for Escort towage has been denied

Name: IceBreaking Operation Requested
Description: A request for IceBreaking Operation has been made

Name: IceBreaking Operation Request Received
Description: A request for IceBreaking Operation has been received

Name: IceBreaking Operation Request Denied
Description: A request for IceBreaking Operation has been denied

Name: Pilotage Request Recieved
Description: Pilot service request has been received

Name: Pilotage Request Denied
Description: Pilot service request has been denied

Name: Towage Requested
Description: Harbour/assistance towage service has been requested

Name: Towage Cancelled
Description: Harbour/assistance towage service has been cancelled

Name: VTS TrafficArea Departure Confirmed
Description: VTS confirms that vessel can departure from Traffic area

Name: VTS TrafficArea Entry Confirmed
Description: VTS confirms that vessel can enter Traffic area

Name: Arrival Vessel Port Confirmed
Description: A port call has been approved for the vessel

Name: Arrival Vessel Port Request Denied
Description: A port call has been denied

Name: Arrival Vessel Port Request Received
Description: A port call has been received

Name: Arrival Vessel Port Requested
Description: A port call has been submitted for a vessel

Name: Arrival Vessel Port Cancelled
Description: A port call has been cancelled
